            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Thank you Klay team ! In just two short months, Klay ( Noida Sec 62) has become a home away from home for my child. The warm and loving environment has made the transition to preschool so smooth and positive.\n\nThe staff at Klay are true gems. They go above and beyond to create a nurturing atmosphere where my child feels safe, secure, and loved.  Their caring nature puts me at ease knowing my child is in good hands.\n\nEven in this short time, I've seen a wonderful change in my child. She is always happy when we pick her up and come home happy and excited to share stories about her day, teachers, and the new friends. It's clear they feel comfortable expressing themselves and exploring their curiosity in this warm and loving environment. Klay's nurturing environment seems to strike the perfect balance between providing comfort and encouraging independence.\n\nPerhaps the most exciting development has been my child's successful toilet training journey.  The teachers and care-givers at Klay provided positive reinforcement and a consistent routine, which made a world of difference. Their patience and understanding throughout this process were invaluable.\n\nThe play-based learning approach at Klay is fantastic.  It allows my child to learn and grow through engaging activities, fostering not just academics but also social and emotional development.\n\nI highly recommend Klay Preschool and Daycare to any parent looking for a nurturing and stimulating environment. In just two months, we've seen incredible growth in our child, and we're so grateful to the entire Klay team- All teacher, Caregivers ! And I look forward to seeing my child continue to blossom at Klay.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
