          "reviewBody": "To give your baby more comfortable, playful, friendly, social, independent and many more good competitive etiquette ,  Klay is the best option for any parent to give the best environment to their babies/toddlers. No doubt the very well trained staff are there who make sure for the cleanliness/ healthy/ comfortable / safe environment around your kid. So now parent can be more relax  about the fact that even the outside of your house, there are people who are as much as responsible as you are for your kid and to give them best development environment to learn things and to grow, in to order to achieve the milestones for your kids.  Much helpful in my case, as I am a working mother of a toddler, and we live nuclear, it’s the best decision we took as a parent for our toddler. Special thanks to Akanksha who was responsible for our onboarding process, it was very helpful and smooth process that we easily onboard our daughter within a sort span of time. At last, thanks to Klay Noida 62 Center for being so good in every aspects of kids development.",
